WEBVTT

1
00:11:13.230 --> 00:11:15.670 
你孤身一人被冲上一座荒岛
You wash up on a deserted island alone.

2
00:11:15.670 --> 00:11:17.410 
沙滩上有一个盒子
Sitting on the sand is a box.

3
00:11:17.410 --> 00:11:19.770 
盒子里有什么
What's in that box?

4
00:11:20.420 --> 00:11:21.760 
那要看小岛的情况来决定...
It would depend on the island...

5
00:11:21.760 --> 00:11:24.650 
它在哪里  有多大  地形什么样
where it is, how big, what's the terrain?

6
00:11:24.650 --> 00:11:25.640 
有淡水吗
Is there fresh water?

7
00:11:25.640 --> 00:11:27.980 
说你脑海中的第一样东西就好
Just say the first thing that comes into your head.

8
00:11:28.120 --> 00:11:29.180 
一把手枪
A pistol.

9
00:11:29.590 --> 00:11:31.100 
神盾局已经不存在了
S.H.I.E.L.D. no longer exists.

10
00:11:31.250 --> 00:11:33.420 
机构已经被标为恐怖组织
The agency has been labeled a terrorist organization.

11
00:11:33.420 --> 00:11:36.710 
你为什么还在这里
So why are you here?

12
00:11:38.390 --> 00:11:40.900 
我是一名特工  这是我的职责
I'm an agent. It's my duty.

13
00:11:43.950 --> 00:11:45.690 
我需要你再重复一遍
I need you to give that to me again.

